CBRE as the exclusive sales agents is pleased to present, Suite 2, 357-359 Military Road, Mosman.

Suite 2, 357-359 Military Road is an office/retail space situated in Mosman's pre-eminent commercial strata building with exposure to the main arterial road. This property boasts a large 371sqm* floor area plus 11 car spaces and comprises a kitchenette, male, female and disabled toilet, as well as a locker room that includes a shower. Large windows around the suite allow for an abundance of light throughout. The property affords a high level of exposure from a large frontage providing significant signage opportunities to Military Road (STCA). This suite is situated in a modern commercial strata building very popular with prestigious businesses and medical professions and is located in a densely populated catchment, with close proximity to express bus services to the CBD. Offered with vacant possession, it presents an exciting opportunity for medical users, office users, retailers or investors (STCA).

The property benefits from the following key
attributes:

• 371sqm* office/retail suite with 11 car spaces
• Offered with vacant possession suitable for medical uses, office uses or retail (STCA)
• Large frontage and opportunity for signage (STCA) to main arterial road
